text: faxinninoy nanu woo Aayootat fayya kaa haak nen, kinnih immay usuk addunya fan kelteeh isi nafsi fayxi kataate, tokkel kay ceelallo Kutay xiiriytek habhabitaah hinnay kaa cabtek habhabitah ceelalloh inna kinni, tamah Naayoota dirabboyse marih ceelallok Nabiyow ku ummatal tatre marih maaqentitte keenil maaq cubbusaah elle kaskassoowa mara yakkeenimkeh
